videos.description: Stephen Carr breaks loose for 50 yard-run then Vavae Malepeai caps off the drive with a 3-yard score.
videos.headline: Trojans' 50-yard run sets them up for score

videos.description: Washington State's James Williams takes it up the middle for a 4-yard touchdown to give his team a 10-7 lead over USC.
videos.headline: Washington St. takes lead on 4-yard rush

videos.description: USC quarterback J.T. Daniels finds his wide receiver Tyler Vaughns for short touchdown that gives USC a 14-10 lead.
videos.headline: Daniels' hooks up with Vaughns for a 9-yard score

videos.description: Washington State wide receiver Easop Winston out runs USC defense for a 28-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Cougars back on top after 28-yard catch-and-run

videos.description: QB Gardner Minshew connects with wide receiver Dezmon Patmon for a 7-yard touchdown and 24-14 lead.
videos.headline: Washington St. strikes again before halftime

videos.description: RB Max Borghi breaks a couple of tackles for a 13-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Cougars' running through Trojans' defense

videos.description: Michael Pittman Jr. takes the short pass all the way to the house and cuts Washington State's lead to only 30-24.
videos.headline: Pittman turns short gain into 50-yard TD

videos.description: JT Daniels finds Amon-Ra St. Brown in the endzone for a 30-yard USC touchdown.
videos.headline: Daniels connects with St. Brown for 30-yard TD

videos.description: Gardner Minshew avoids pressure and connects with Easop Winston for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Minshew scrambles and finds Winston for TD

videos.description: Vavae Malepeai runs up the middle for a 2-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Malepeai punches in 2-yard TD

videos.description: USC DL Jay Tufele blocks Blake Mazza's 38-yard field-goal attempt as USC hangs on to win 39-36.
videos.headline: USC blocks Washington St.'s game-tying FG

videos.description: Washington State's Logan Tago hit USC QB JT Daniels in the head on a play earlier this season but no targeting was called.
